tommy_uint32_t tommy_hash_u32 ( tommy_uint32_t  init_val,
const void *  void_key,
tommy_size_t  key_len 
)

Hash function.

Robert Jenkins "lookup3" hash, from http://www.burtleburtle.net/bob/hash/doobs.html, function hashlittle().

Note:
This function is platform independent as it read always in little endian format.
Parameters:
init_valInitial value. You can use this to concatenate hash. Otherwise set it at 0.
void_keyKey to hash.
key_lenLength of the key.
Returns:
The 32 bit hash value.
